Sign Up For Our Vocal Auditions Today!

We are actively looking for singers ages 8 to 25 to:

  • Record with Multi-Platinum Grammy Award winning producers and songwriters
  • Be directed on a Music Video on set with film crew, lights & cameras
  • Work with celebrities, top choreographers, and producers in Music!
  • Have the opportunity to be signed by a Record Label
  • Be on a Red Carpet with your favorite Stars
  • Much Much more!!

Enter your information below and we will send you the Audition information
